com.is2300.jedi.edi.global

Class EDIEnvelope

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.is2300.jedi.edi.global.EDIEnvelope

  • public class EDIEnvelope
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class which includes the following classes:
    • InterchangeCtlHdr

      The responsible class for Interchange Control Header data.

    • FunctionalGrpHdr

      The responsible class for Functional Group Control Header data.

    • TransactionSetHdr

      The responsible class for Transaction Set Control Header data.

    • TransactionSetTrlr

      The responsible class for Transaction Set Control Trailer data.

    • FunctionalGrpTrlr

      The responsible class for Functional Group Control Trailer data.

    • InterchangeCtlTrlr

      The responsible class for Interchange Control Trailer data.

    This class provides methods for validating the trailers to the headers of the various sections of an EDI document listed above. By performing this data validation, the program can be certain that the data received is the same as the data that was sent by the trading partner.

    Furthermore, this class provides the methods required to set up and maintain an audit trail of all EDI transmissions received and sent between the two trading partners, based upon the trading partner identification numbers contained within the EDI transmissions.

    Since:
    0.5.0
    Version:
    0.5.0
    Author:
    Sean Carrick

                                 int field)

        Parameters:
        qualifier - the Interchange ID Qualifier from the incoming EDI file

        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the data provided does not meet the requirements listed above for either of the two (2) parameters required

        Parameters:

        Returns:
